                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-80-off415 t17860222-80-cd416"></join> last, one linen shirt, value 1 s. one pair of worsted stockings, value 1 s. one pair of thread ditto, value 6 d. one pair of cotton ditto, value 6 d. two pair of woollen drawers, value 1 s. three caps, value 1 s. one muslin ruffle, value 1 s. one stock, value 6 d. one box, value 18 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
